edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.io.coursera.converter

Class CourseraConverterService

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.io.coursera.converter.CourseraConverterService

  • @Service
 @Transactional(propagation=REQUIRED,
               readOnly=false)
public class CourseraConverterService
extends Object
    This converter service maps Coursera forum data from a coursera database to DiscourseDB. The connection to the coursera database is established by the calling class, which has to pass a database access object to the methods in this service class. Mapping methods are executed transactionally.
    Author:
    Haitian Gong, Oliver Ferschke
